  with. Please make sure you and your friend list each other when prompted 
 during registration. Chains of friends are not permitted.\n\nFAQ\n\nI don
 't have a team\, can I still play?\nYes\, register as an Individual and we
  will place you with a team.\n\nI will miss a few weeks\, can I still play
 ?\nYes\, all teams have extra players on them just in case you're absent o
 n a given week. Teams can also use substitute players.\n\nHow do I make su
 re my friend and I play on the same team?\nDuring registration there is a 
 field where you can list the friend you want to play with and the league w
 ill place you together.\n\nI don't know how to play or don't think I'll be
  very good\, should I play?\nYes\, join our Wednesday or Friday Night leag
 ues aimed at new and developing players and you will learn the basics in a
  fun\, encouraging environment.\n\nI'm not LGBTQ+\, can I still play?\nYes
 \, we are accepting to all people as long as you consider yourself an ally
  to our community.\n\nMore info: https://outsportsleague.leagueapps.com/le
 agues/volleyball-(indoor)/5048670-fridays---draftremix-league-abcd
LOCATION:Dover Shores Community Center
URL:https://outsportsleague.leagueapps.com/leagues/volleyball-(indoor)/504
 8670-fridays---draftremix-league-abcd
END:VEVENT
